&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;12+ years of experience in software engineering and technical leadership, ideally in consulting, pre-sales, or account development within technology or digital services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with solution architecture, software architecture, cloud platforms, and AI native software engineering practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Can conduct effective workshops, exploring potential use cases, explaining trade-offs in solutions &amp;amp; aligning stakeholders on what is the optimal solution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possess working proficiency in at least one programming language (e.g. Python, JavaScript)&lt;/li&gt;
