&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advise enterprise customers on how to adopt and operationalise AI in ways that create measurable business impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead executive workshops and discovery engagements focused on new digital products, AI strategy, AI use case identification &amp;amp; prioritisation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help organisations identify high-value AI opportunities across customer experience, operations, software delivery, modernization and internal platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tailor AI conversations and narratives based on the enterprise&#39;s current AI maturity curve.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
